Output docs/assets/demo.gif
Set Theme "Catppuccin Latte"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1200
Set Height 800
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set BorderRadius 10

Hide
Type "./bin/swarm"
Enter
Sleep 300ms
Show

Sleep 2s

Type "Hello, what can you do?"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 8s

Type "! ls -l"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "!"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "/skills"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 10s

Type "How many Go files are in this repository?"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 20s
